# Example of future use:
from SHAPInteractiveManager import SHAPInteractiveManager

model = SafeResNet18(num_classes=4)
model.load_state_dict(torch.load('outputs_tcc_resnet18/resnet18_model.pth'))
shap_manager = SHAPInteractiveManager(model, DEVICE, class_names, SHAP_ANALYSIS_DIR)

# Analyze new image
image_tensor, image_path = shap_manager.get_image_by_path("your_image.jpg")
result = shap_manager.analyze_single_image(image_tensor, image_path, "new_analysis")
